Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveSuspected fraudster, Ramon Abbas, popularly known as Hushpuppi, has become a subject of trend on Twitter, hours after singer, Lojay, released the remix of his hit single, Monalisa, featuring Chris Brown.
In his verse on the remix, Chris Brown sang, “See for this life | Me and you chop like Hushpuppi | We walk and they stare | Please show them you’re best…”
Tweeps have been reacting to the Hushpuppi reference in the song.
Edo Boy said, “Chris Brown confirm am say hushpuppi chop life.”
Another tweep, Ebenezer Ekpeyong said, “I listened to Monalisa remix and I heard Chris Brown mentioned Hushpuppi. The guy just reminds us of the Oga kpata kpata.”
